--------------- System Msnagment ( Process ) ---------------------------------------------------
1. systemctl list-units --type = services = It show all the services.
2. systemctl start service name = It start the service.
3. systemctl stop service name = It stop the service.
4. systemctl status service name = It show the status of service.
